414
00:28:58,187 --> 00:29:00,049
<font color="#ffff00">Jake estava certo.</font>

415
00:29:00,507 --> 00:29:02,623
<font color="#ffff00">Revelaria o melhor de nós.</font>

416
00:29:16,968 --> 00:29:19,246
